{"tid":584092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉鳴煒︰派錢不能解決問題，不是所有問題可用錢解決。","createTime":"2018-03-07T14:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T03:08:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":96,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"5f333e5e08e27aaa743ed0ecc5e678c02937e22b","tid":584092,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】青年事務委員會完成香港青年發展策略公眾參與的報告書，主席劉鳴煒表示，報告如實反映青年人在就業和置業等各方面的意見。被問到很多青年覺得未能受惠於政府的政策，包括預算案的派糖措施，劉鳴煒認為不是所有問題可用錢解決。<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗亦有出席委員會會議，他說早前推出的青年委員自薦試行計劃極之成功，質素非常高，令他對青年人改觀，而今次報告書將成為未來成立的青年發展委員會的工作基礎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=256480\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D256480&d=dANmUINyULLXl1SVtOyhv9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a57a2f75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D256480&h=6c2b7081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=256480</a>"},{"pid":"501eb41044657590968f40247d0bc41a07b65c37","tid":584092,"uid":106363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:33:11.000Z","msg":"佢係咪講緊自己呀"},{"pid":"7afefec1384c3f30364fe4b6c5109f4ec556351a","tid":584092,"uid":141072,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:41:39.000Z","msg":"每次一有中產或以上既人講依句出黎真係想衝埋去打佢地一鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70125e60ce8e954d886679264aa886ce97b5d5d","tid":584092,"uid":38671,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:43:24.000Z","msg":"係佢階層就無錯<br />\n煩既野唔會係錢既問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33e5708e448e3f48429c6f46a24b1e34f15d810","tid":584092,"uid":124585,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"你願唔願意去